Class GlossaryTermElement

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.AttributedMetadataElement
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.GlossaryTermElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
CorrelatedMetadataElement, MetadataElement
public class GlossaryTermElement extends AttributedMetadataElement implements CorrelatedMetadataElement
GlossaryTermElement contains the properties and header for a glossary term entity retrieved from the metadata repository.
